Creating a new LoUIE project

* From the command line:

+-----+
mvn archetype:generate -DarchetypeGroupId='com.rhythm.louie' -DarchetypeArtifactId='louie-archetype' -DarchetypeVersion='1.9-SNAPSHOT'

Define value for property 'groupId': : com.somecompany
Define value for property 'artifactId': : sample
Define value for property 'version':  1.0-SNAPSHOT: :
Define value for property 'package':  com.somecompany: :
Define value for property 'service_lowercase':  : : sample
Define value for property 'service_titlecase':  : : Sample

+-----+

* OR From NetBeans:


