 <<In NetBeans, create a New Project>>

[./images/create/nb_from_arch.png] 

 <<Create a new Maven project from a Maven Archetype>>

[./images/create/nb_arch_filter.png] 

 <<Filter the archetypes using the keyword "louie" and select the latest version>>

[./images/create/nb_arch_args.png] 

 <<Populate the arguments: Project Name, Group Id, service_lowercase and service_titlecase>>

[./images/create/nb_generated.png]

 <<You should now have three new generated projects>>

[./images/create/nb_clean_build.png]

 <<The Services project will appear to have errors, so clean and build the main project>>

